  "frontCover": "Front cover of a greeting card in a soft watercolor style. The scene depicts a picturesque campus setting with Mediterranean-inspired architecture, featuring buildings with orange tiled roofs and a prominent bell tower in the background. Tall palm trees are scattered throughout the scene, framing the view. The sky is a gentle blend of pastel blues, pinks, and oranges, suggesting a warm, inviting atmosphere. In the foreground, a charming, plump cartoon green dinosaur with big black eyes and rosy cheeks stands on a grassy lawn. The dinosaur is holding a small, square card with a bright red heart on it. The overall color palette is light and airy, dominated by soft greens, warm beiges, and pale blues and oranges. The text \"Ari Tal\" is displayed prominently at the top in an elegant, flowing cursive script, with the smaller text \"AI For Good Conference Campus CA | June 2025\" positioned below it in a clean, sans-serif font. The artistic style is whimsical, charming, and professional, with gentle brushstrokes and a soft, diffused lighting.",
